M||name|vc-rc-best-practices
M||desc|>-
M||tx|rc and nx.js perf op guidelines from vc Engineering. This skill shd be used when writing, reviewing, or refactoring rc/nx.js code to ensure optimal perf patterns. Triggers on tasks involving rc cp, nx.js pages, data fetching, bundle op, or perf improvements.
