M||tx|---
M|Verc|tx|Comprehensive perf op guide for rc and nx.js applications, maintained by vc. Contains 69 rules across 8 categories, prioritized by impact to guide automated refactoring and code generation.
M|When|Refe|
M|When|it|Writing new rc cp or nx.js pages
M|When|it|Implementing data fetching (client or server-side)
M|When|it|Reviewing code for perf issues
M|When|it|Refactoring existing rc/nx.js code
M|When|it|Optimizing bundle size or load times
M|Rule|tx|\| Priority \| Category \| Impact \| Prefix \|
M|Rule|tx|\|----------\|----------\|--------\|--------\|
M|Rule|tx|\| 1 \| Eliminating Waterfalls \| ct \| `async-` \|
M|Rule|tx|\| 2 \| Bundle Size op \| ct \| `bundle-` \|
M|Rule|tx|\| 3 \| Server-Side perf \| hi \| `server-` \|
M|Rule|tx|\| 4 \| Client-Side Data Fetching \| md-hi \| `client-` \|
M|Rule|tx|\| 5 \| Re-render op \| md \| `rerender-` \|
M|Rule|tx|\| 6 \| Rendering perf \| md \| `rendering-` \|
M|Rule|tx|\| 7 \| JavaScript perf \| lo-md \| `js-` \|
M|Rule|tx|\| 8 \| Advanced Patterns \| lo \| `advanced-` \|
M|1. E|it|`async-cheap-condition-before-await` - Check cheap sync conditions before awaiting flags or remote values
M|1. E|it|`async-defer-await` - Move await into branches where actually used
M|1. E|it|`async-parallel` - Use Promise.all() for independent operations
M|1. E|it|`async-dependencies` - Use better-all for partial dependencies
M|1. E|it|`async-ap-rt` - Start promises early, await late in ap rt
M|1. E|it|`async-suspense-boundaries` - Use Suspense to stream cn
M|2. B|it|`bundle-barrel-imports` - Import directly, avoid barrel files
M|2. B|it|`bundle-dynamic-imports` - Use nx/dynamic for heavy cp
M|2. B|it|`bundle-defer-third-party` - Load an/logging after hydration
M|2. B|it|`bundle-conditional` - Load modules only when feature is activated
M|2. B|it|`bundle-preload` - Preload on hover/focus for perceived speed
M|3. S|it|`server-auth-actions` - Authenticate server actions like ap rt
M|3. S|it|`server-cache-rc` - Use rc.cache() for per-request deduplication
M|3. S|it|`server-cache-lru` - Use LRU cache for cross-request caching
M|3. S|it|`server-dedup-props` - Avoid duplicate serialization in RSC props
M|3. S|it|`server-hoist-static-io` - Hoist static I/O (fonts, logos) to md level
M|3. S|it|`server-no-shared-md-state` - Avoid md-level mutable request state in RSC/SSR
M|3. S|it|`server-serialization` - Minimize data passed to client cp
M|3. S|it|`server-parallel-fetching` - Restructure cp to parallelize fetches
M|3. S|it|`server-parallel-nested-fetching` - Chain nested fetches per item in Promise.all
M|3. S|it|`server-after-nonblocking` - Use after() for non-blocking operations
M|4. C|it|`client-swr-dedup` - Use SWR for automatic request deduplication
M|4. C|it|`client-event-listeners` - Deduplicate global event listeners
M|4. C|it|`client-passive-event-listeners` - Use passive listeners for scroll
M|4. C|it|`client-localstorage-sc` - Version and minimize localStorage data
M|5. R|it|`rerender-defer-reads` - Don't subscribe to state only used in callbacks
M|5. R|it|`rerender-memo` - Extract expensive work into memoized cp
M|5. R|it|`rerender-memo-w/-default-value` - Hoist default non-primitive props
M|5. R|it|`rerender-dependencies` - Use primitive dependencies in effects
M|5. R|it|`rerender-derived-state` - Subscribe to derived booleans, not raw values
M|5. R|it|`rerender-derived-state-no-effect` - Derive state during render, not effects
M|5. R|it|`rerender-functional-setstate` - Use functional setState for stable callbacks
M|5. R|it|`rerender-lazy-state-init` - Pass fn to useState for expensive values
M|5. R|it|`rerender-simple-expression-in-memo` - Avoid memo for simple primitives
M|5. R|it|`rerender-split-combined-hooks` - Split hooks w/ independent dependencies
M|5. R|it|`rerender-move-effect-to-event` - Put interaction logic in event handlers
M|5. R|it|`rerender-transitions` - Use startTransition for non-ur updates
M|5. R|it|`rerender-use-deferred-value` - Defer expensive renders to keep input responsive
M|5. R|it|`rerender-use-ref-transient-values` - Use refs for transient frequent values
M|5. R|it|`rerender-no-inline-cp` - Don't define cp inside cp
M|6. R|it|`rendering-animate-svg-wrapper` - Animate div wrapper, not SVG element
M|6. R|it|`rendering-cn-visibility` - Use cn-visibility for long lists
M|6. R|it|`rendering-hoist-jsx` - Extract static JSX outside cp
M|6. R|it|`rendering-svg-precision` - Reduce SVG coordinate precision
M|6. R|it|`rendering-hydration-no-flicker` - Use inline script for client-only data
M|6. R|it|`rendering-hydration-suppress-wn` - Suppress expected mismatches
M|6. R|it|`rendering-activity` - Use Activity cp for show/hide
M|6. R|it|`rendering-conditional-render` - Use ternary, not && for conditionals
M|6. R|it|`rendering-usetransition-loading` - Prefer useTransition for loading state
M|6. R|it|`rendering-resource-hints` - Use rc DOM resource hints for preloading
M|6. R|it|`rendering-script-defer-async` - Use defer or async on script tags
M|7. J|it|`js-batch-dom-css` - Group CSS changes via classes or cssText
M|7. J|it|`js-index-maps` - bd Map for repeated lookups
M|7. J|it|`js-cache-property-access` - Cache object properties in loops
M|7. J|it|`js-cache-fn-results` - Cache fn results in md-level Map
M|7. J|it|`js-cache-storage` - Cache localStorage/sessionStorage reads
M|7. J|it|`js-combine-iterations` - Combine multiple filter/map into one loop
M|7. J|it|`js-length-check-first` - Check array length before expensive comparison
M|7. J|it|`js-early-exit` - Return early from functions
M|7. J|it|`js-hoist-regexp` - Hoist RegExp creation outside loops
M|7. J|it|`js-min-max-loop` - Use loop for min/max instead of sort
M|7. J|it|`js-set-map-lookups` - Use Set/Map for O(1) lookups
M|7. J|it|`js-tosorted-immutable` - Use toSorted() for immutability
M|7. J|it|`js-flatmap-filter` - Use flatMap to map and filter in one pass
M|7. J|it|`js-request-idle-callback` - Defer non-ct work to browser idle time
M|8. A|it|`advanced-effect-event-deps` - Don't put `useEffectEvent` results in effect deps
M|8. A|it|`advanced-event-handler-refs` - Store event handlers in refs
M|8. A|it|`advanced-init-once` - Initialize app once per app load
M|8. A|it|`advanced-use-latest` - useLatest for stable callback refs
